      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLESSED RAIN (7) was never in contention last time after settling off pace at this track, but prior to that won easily by 9 lengths at this track (21.59) beating Paw Bastow in a Free For All on March 9. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and two minor placings from eight starts. Rates on top in this line up. ESSENCE (3) has shown good improvement at her last two starts, breaking through last time at Healesville over 300m. Form from her last run is proving strong. One of the key runners again. PAW ESTRELLA (1) has a strong record this journey here with three wins and a minor from six starts. Placed last time (22.08) at Ballarat in a Mix 3/4, finishing third and beaten half a length. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. DOCHERTY (8) dominated last start. Big chance on that form.",
